{"body": "I don't have _much_ more to say on the subject except that I think that the benefits of this change far out weighs the costs.  It allows developers to solve a problem that otherwise is unsolvable in a centralized, e.g. DRY, way.  Further, I feel that the percentage of apps that use `before_add` is small and those that are either intentionally or unintentionally returning false is most likely minuscule.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/2023630", "created_at": "2011-09-06T23:16:33Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/2881#issuecomment-2023630", "updated_at": "2011-09-06T23:16:33Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 2881, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/shwoodard/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/shwoodard/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/shwoodard/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/shwoodard", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/shwoodard/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/shwoodard", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/shwoodard/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/1e2f907b5827a6f705d61c04d5e24bfc?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F1f42e9148d92052e09e08f8874979d12.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/shwoodard/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/shwoodard/received_events", "gravatar_id": "1e2f907b5827a6f705d61c04d5e24bfc", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/shwoodard/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "shwoodard", "type": "User", "id": 34149, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/shwoodard/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "52383e10bd3543c15101055d"}, "id": 2023630, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/2881"}
